  "body": "Use web search to find REAL practice/exam questions on these topics, then return them as items tagged to the concept(s) they test, each with its answer key and a source pointer (kind 'web', ref = the page URL). Prefer real, vetted questions (textbook problem sets, past exams, reputable practice sites) over anything you invent. Only include questions you actually found, with their source.",
